citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 10:50 am to
12:10 pm on 21-JUN-17.
Inspectors arrived at 10:50 am to a locked gate. Inspector called out for licensee and called both listed numbers
and left messages. Inspectors attempted to contact licensee from 10:50
am to 12: pm.
